aily.com/local/realtime/article/20180430/58137715</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">如果說一個成功的男人背後總有一個偉大的女人，清潔龍阿德的背後就有五個人。他們是來自科域盈創（Fevaworks Solutions）的團隊，包括內容營銷總監Rondo、設計師及導演Ruck、負責美術設計的Rain、動畫製作的Debbie，以及擔任阿德聲優的Ceci。自去年團隊成功投標後，五人從去年六月起經營清潔龍阿德的facebook專頁，每月至少推出10個帖文，向港人宣揚清潔香港的訊息。在這近一年半間，他們已為專頁帶來快近20,000個like。</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181128/20556111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181128%2F20556111&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfaZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=120e27ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181128%2F20556111&h=d1c150a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181128/20556111</a>"},{"pid":"8ca4507ef6517761ba1d53dad0ab8507b9af8db0","tid":1037684,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be987e4e1c510130ca202ec26554ac12bcae744a","tid":1037684,"uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"東江登Fevawork直情接政府Project幫政府宣傳添，咁又夠唔夠紅呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">另外，「Fevaworks Solutions（Hong Kong）Limited」（科域盈創（香港）有限公司）亦以355萬元獲聘負責製作電視及電台宣傳片、短片、動畫並作跨媒體平台宣傳工作，該公司董事為柳宇澄，他亦是股東之一，而柳與前政助羅永聰均為曾俊華競選辦成員之一。</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180430/58137715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F58137715&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfaZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=e828b459\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F58137715&h=6ed38ed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180430/58137715</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">如果說一個成功的男人背後總有一個偉大的女人，